data.description: Welcome to 162 Spruce Grove Rd in desirable Colerain Twp.  Finally, a home on a large lot is available that requires no updating!  If you are looking for multiple acres with privacy, your search ends here.  A long flat driveway leads you to the one of a kind raised rancher.  As you approach the home, take notice of the recent exterior improvements including roof, vinyl siding, replacement windows and doors, and custom wrap around deck!  Prepare to be wowed because more upgrades await inside.  The main level features a grand great room with vaulted ceilings, exposed beams, and floor to ceiling stone fireplace.  The level is highlighted by the spacious primary bedroom suite with beautiful full bath.  2 additional generously sized bedrooms and hall bath complete the level.  You will find more value downstairs with a cozy family room, dining area, kitchen, full bath, laundry, and garage access.  The lower level is highlighted by the custom kitchen.  No expense was spared and no detail was overlooked.  It's a chef's dream with stainless appliances, granite counters, soft close drawers and doors, backsplash, and recessed lighting.  Need outdoor space?  The huge wrap around composite deck is a great space for entertaining.  Under the deck, you'll find the patios for even more outdoor living space.  Need more value?  There are two outbuilding with electric and the utility costs are extremely low with the significant credits earned by the solar panels.  All this plus low taxes in a convenient location make this property a must see.  Act quickly on this amazing opportunity!
